<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="appropriate-adj">appropriate <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'prəʊpriət/    美 /ə'proʊpriət/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>恰当的；适当的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His casual clothes were not <strong>appropriate for</strong> such a formal occasion.
他随便的穿着不适合这样正式的场合。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I didn’t feel that this was an <strong>appropriate time</strong> / <strong>place</strong> to mention the subject.
我觉得这个时候/地方不适合提这个话题。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>appropriately /ə'proʊpriət/ adv   </p></div>